{"title":"庄稼人与禾苗（外一首）","authors":["厉彦林"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":4,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄稼人与禾苗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"厉彦林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨水贵如油"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄稼人扔掉蓑衣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俯下身子，凝聚目光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看圆圆的水珠相互追赶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从叶流到茎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从茎流到根"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流进土地干裂的唇齿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谷子苗善解人意"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱雨如命，顾不上喘气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忙着扎根"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忙着长骨头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忙着抽穗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨点声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拔节声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在农时最深处默契"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此时，庄稼人已拔不动脚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双脚与谷根"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧紧地攀结在一起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"端午时节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日子乍暖还寒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土生土长的庄稼人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不懂兮兮斯斯的《楚辞》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咽口粽子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扔掉厚棉衣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大步跨出插束艾草的门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶着黄牛、木犁和播种谣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"匆匆忙忙下地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田野上凉风嗖嗖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"墒沟里弥漫寒气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是庄稼人的大刹鞋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏酥了初醒的田埂"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}